channel.title: [HELP]Every client[/HELP]
channel.description:
Hey, I have a problem with almost every downloaded client I download.
This is what happens to them all, but the IP changes from clients, obv.
[img]http://i53.tinypic.com/29gimuo.png[/img]
Please help me, thanks.

item.title: [HELP]Every client[/HELP]
item.dc:creator: @Aceron4 Aceron4
item.description:
@Aceron4 wrote:

Your client folder should have a .jar file in it called Z-filesearcher. Open that up and search for that no-ip that is showing up in your cmd picture. The z-filesearcher will tell you what file its in and on what line. Just open up the file it shows you. And replace that no-ip with your no-ip

P.S. If you dont have Z-FileSearcher download it here.
